data.description: Incredible 5-bedroom ranch-style residence boasting a spacious patio and a covered deck for seamless indoor-outdoor living. The walk-out basement adds to the allure, making it an ideal space for hosting gatherings and events. This remarkable home is graced with exquisite hardwood flooring, luxurious granite countertops, a generously sized kitchen island, and a grand master bathroom complete with a spacious shower. The fully finished basement includes two additional bedrooms, a full bathroom, and an expansive family room for added comfort and functionality. Discover the  this exceptional home – where comfort, style, and space unite to create your dream retreat.
